an class="toc-text">使用Let’s Encrypt签发SSL证书</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8acme-sh"><span class="toc-number">4.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">使用acme.sh</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></div></div><div class="card-widget card-recent-post"><div class="item-headline"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-history"></i><span>最近发布</span></div><div class="aside-list"><div class="aside-list-item"><a class="thumbnail" href="/archives/tdesign-miniprogram-dark" title="TDesign 小程序暗黑模式适配"><img src= "data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" onerror="this.onerror=null,this.src=&quot;/img/404.jpg&quot;" data-lazy-src="https://img.neosey.com/post/H1.png" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='/img/404.jpg'" alt="TDesign 小程序暗黑模式适配"/></a><div class="content"><a class="title" href="/archives/tdesign-miniprogram-dark" title="TDesign 小程序暗黑模式适配">TDesign 小程序暗黑模式适配</a><time datetime="2024-04-22T16:00:00.000Z" title="发表于 2024-04-23 00:00:00">2024-04-23</time></div></div><div class="aside-list-item"><a class="thumbnail" href="/archives/69" title="Ubuntu 修复Sub-process /usr/bin/dpkg returned an error code (1)报错"><img src= "data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" onerror="this.onerror=null,this.src=&quot;/img/404.jpg&quot;" data-lazy-src="/img/default_cover.jpg" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='/img/404.jpg'" alt="Ubuntu 修复Sub-process /usr/bin/dpkg returned an error code (1)报错"/></a><div class="content"><a class="title" href="/archives/69" title="Ubuntu 修复Sub-process /usr/bin/dpkg returned an error code (1)报错">Ubuntu 修复Sub-process /usr/bin/dpkg returned an error code (1)报错</a><time datetime="2024-02-01T01:00:00.000Z" title="发表于 2024-02-01 09:00:00">2024-02-01</time></div></div><div class="aside-list-item"><a class="thumbnail" href="/archives/70" title="国内开源镜像站"><img src= "data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAA